      "html": "\n      <header class=\"site-header\">\n        <a class=\"brand\" href=\"index.html\" aria-label=\"AI DRI 指南针首页\">\n          <span class=\"brand-mark compass-mark\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n            <svg viewBox=\"0 0 44 44\" role=\"img\">\n              <circle cx=\"22\" cy=\"22\" r=\"18\"></circle>\n              <path d=\"M26.8 17.2 23.9 29l-6.7-2.2 2.9-11.8 6.7 2.2Z\"></path>\n              <path d=\"M20.1 15 17.2 26.8l6.7 2.2 2.9-11.8-6.7-2.2Z\"></path>\n              <path d=\"M22 5v5M22 34v5M5 22h5M34 22h5\"></path>\n            </svg>\n          </span>\n          <span>AI DRI 指南针</span>\n        </a>\n        <nav class=\"nav\" aria-label=\"主导航\">\n          <a data-nav-key=\"guide\" href=\"guide.html\">核心概念</a>\n          <a data-nav-key=\"map\" href=\"map.html\">能力地图</a>\n          <a data-nav-key=\"cases\" href=\"cases.html\">常见误区</a>\n          <a data-nav-key=\"resources\" href=\"resources.html\">成长路径</a>\n          <a data-nav-key=\"about\" href=\"index.html#about\">关于我们</a>\n        </nav>\n        <div class=\"editor-bar\" aria-label=\"编辑工具栏\">\n          <button class=\"editor-button editor-primary\" type=\"button\" id=\"toggleEdit\">编辑模式<span aria-hidden=\"true\">›</span>\n          </button>\n          <button class=\"editor-button\" id=\"saveLocal\" type=\"button\">保存本机</button><button class=\"editor-button\" type=\"button\" id=\"savePage\">发布云端</button>\n          <button class=\"editor-button\" id=\"refreshCloud\" type=\"button\">从云端刷新</button><button class=\"editor-button\" type=\"button\" id=\"exportHtml\">导出 HTML</button>\n          <button class=\"editor-button\" id=\"cloudSettings\" type=\"button\">GitHub 已连接</button><span class=\"save-status\" id=\"saveStatus\" aria-live=\"polite\"></span>\n        </div>\n      </header>\n\n      <main id=\"top\">\n        <section class=\"hero\" aria-labelledby=\"hero-title\">\n          <div class=\"hero-copy\">\n            <p class=\"pill\">AI 时代能力升级</p>\n            <h1 id=\"hero-title\">从会用 AI，<br>到成为 AI 时代的 DRI</h1>\n            <p class=\"hero-text\">\n              AI 时代的 DRI，不是把任务交给 AI 的人，而是能真实业务目标和价值为\n              AI 明确边界、可评估、可迭代，并产生可沉淀资产和复利效应的人。\n            </p>\n            <p class=\"hero-text\"><br></p>\n            <div class=\"hero-actions\">\n              <a class=\"button primary\" href=\"#dri\">开始导览 <span aria-hidden=\"true\">→</span></a>\n              <a class=\"button secondary\" href=\"#assessment\">先做自测</a>\n            </div>\n            <a class=\"scroll-hint\" href=\"#assessment\">\n              <span aria-hidden=\"true\">↓</span>\n              往下滚动查看更多\n            </a>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"hero-media single-media\" aria-label=\"AI DRI 能力地图图片区\">\n            <article class=\"hero-visual-card\">\n              <img data-editable-image=\"\" src=\"assets/home-hero.gif\" alt=\"AI DRI 问题定义导览动效\">\n            </article>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"assessment\" class=\"assessment section-card\" aria-labelledby=\"assessment-title\">\n          <div class=\"section-heading\">\n            <h2 id=\"assessment-title\">先做一个 AITI 人格测试</h2>\n            <p>回答 10 个场景题，生成你的 AI DRI 人格画像。</p>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"quiz-stage\">\n            <button class=\"round-nav prev\" type=\"button\" id=\"prevQuestion\" aria-label=\"上一题\">←</button>\n            <article class=\"quiz-card ghost left\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <p>第 10 / 10 题</p>\n              <h3>当 AI 能力要从 Demo 走向稳定复用时，你会优先补什么？</h3>\n            </article>\n\n            <article class=\"quiz-card active\" aria-live=\"polite\">\n              <p class=\"quiz-count\" id=\"quizCount\">第 1 / 10 题</p>\n              <h3 id=\"quizQuestion\">场景：业务同学提出“能不能用 AI 做一个自动生成短视频脚本的功能”，希望你当天给出初步判断。你最可能先怎么做？</h3>\n              <div class=\"options\" id=\"quizOptions\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"option\" data-level=\"1\">A. 先找几个主流 AI 工具试一下，让模型生成几版脚本，看看效果是否像样；同时请算法或工程同学帮忙判断大概能不能做。</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"option\" data-level=\"2\">B. 先拆清楚任务类型、输入输出、风格控制和结构化要求；再比较 Prompt、工作流、微调等方案的成本、效果和边界。</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"option\" data-level=\"3\">C. 先判断这个能力在业务链路里的长期价值，再反推技术路线、数据需求、评测方式和阶段性投入节奏。</button></div>\n            </article>\n\n            <article class=\"quiz-card ghost right\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n              <p>第 2 / 10 题</p>\n              <h3>一个 AI Demo 看起来效果不错，准备上线前你最关注什么？</h3>\n            </article>\n            <button class=\"round-nav next\" type=\"button\" id=\"nextQuestion\" aria-label=\"下一题\">→</button>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"quiz-dots\" id=\"quizDots\" aria-label=\"题目进度\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"active\" aria-label=\"跳转到第 1 题\"></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"\" aria-label=\"跳转到第 2 题\"></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"\" aria-label=\"跳转到第 3 题\"></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"\" aria-label=\"跳转到第 4 题\"></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"\" aria-label=\"跳转到第 5 题\"></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"\" aria-label=\"跳转到第 6 题\"></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"\" aria-label=\"跳转到第 7 题\"></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"\" aria-label=\"跳转到第 8 题\"></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"\" aria-label=\"跳转到第 9 题\"></button><button type=\"button\" class=\"\" aria-label=\"跳转到第 10 题\"></button></div>\n          <article class=\"quiz-result\" id=\"quizResult\" aria-live=\"polite\" hidden=\"\">\n            <div class=\"result-medal\" aria-hidden=\"true\">✦</div>\n            <div>\n              <p class=\"result-kicker\">AITI 人格已生成</p>\n              <h3>你的 AITI 人格：<span id=\"resultLevel\">选型者 × 操盘手 × 流程师 × 主导型 DRI</span></h3>\n              <p id=\"resultCopy\">\n                完成 10 道题后，将展示四层能力标签、核心能力得分、长板与短板。\n              </p>\n            </div>\n          </article>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"dri\" class=\"dri-section section-card\" aria-labelledby=\"dri-title\">\n          <div class=\"section-heading\">\n            <h2 id=\"dri-title\">DRI 到底是什么</h2>\n            <p>这一份专门澄清误区</p>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"definition-grid\">\n            <article class=\"definition-panel negative\">\n              <h3><span aria-hidden=\"true\">×</span> DRI 不是</h3>\n              <ul>\n                <li>仅用 AI 工具的人</li>\n                <li>会写 Prompt 的人</li>\n                <li>被动 Demo 的人</li>\n                <li>把任务交给模型就完事的人</li>\n                <li>模仿最佳实践的人</li>\n              </ul>\n            </article>\n\n            <div class=\"definition-arrow\" aria-hidden=\"true\">····→</div>\n\n            <article class=\"definition-panel positive\">\n              <h3><span aria-hidden=\"true\">✓</span> DRI 是</h3>\n              <ul>\n                <li>能定义真实业务问题的人</li>\n                <li>能拆解 AI 最适合介入的人</li>\n                <li>能制定假设、设定可量化 KPI 的人</li>\n                <li>能设计 Agent 或工作流的人</li>\n                <li>能评估产出、发现价值偏差的人</li>\n                <li>能复盘迭代、复利沉淀的人</li>\n              </ul>\n              <div class=\"definition-tags\" aria-label=\"定义详情\">\n                <button type=\"button\" class=\"tag-popover tag-row-1\" data-popover=\"problem\">问题定义</button>\n                <button type=\"button\" class=\"tag-popover tag-row-2\" data-popover=\"collab\">AI 协同素养</button>\n                <button type=\"button\" class=\"tag-popover tag-row-4\" data-popover=\"agent\">Agent 应用力</button>\n                <button type=\"button\" class=\"tag-popover tag-row-5\" data-popover=\"evaluate\">评估 / 优化</button>\n                <button type=\"button\" class=\"tag-popover tag-row-6\" data-popover=\"launch\">上线迭代</button>\n              </div>\n            </article>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"core-definition\">\n            <span aria-hidden=\"true\">★</span>\n            <strong>核心定义</strong>\n            <p>AI 时代 DRI = 对 AI 价值闭环直接负责的人</p>\n          </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"resources\" class=\"why-section section-card\" aria-labelledby=\"why-title\">\n          <h2 id=\"why-title\">为什么需要这套指南针</h2>\n          <div id=\"about\" class=\"faq-list\">\n            <details open=\"\">\n              <summary><span>给你一个真实的用户反馈（来自一增长方向 PM 的分享）</span><span class=\"faq-plus\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span></summary>\n              <p></p><div data-page-id=\"Y4cjdp8M2oYvrUxOMAacYf7JnJd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\"><div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn8fiZxDs1WrdKvS33NgNqhg\"><strong>岗位</strong><b>日常工作</b>：用户拉新策略、留存实验、增长模型迭代</div><div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn8fiZxDs1WrdKvS33NgNqhg\"><b>AITI人格测试结果：</b><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;\">识图者 × 守门员 × 提效者 × 参与型 DRI</span></div><div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn8fiZxDs1WrdKvS33NgNqhg\"><b>如何成为一个优秀的DRI反馈：</b>先补全短板且刚需的能力，再考虑扩展能力</div><div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn8fiZxDs1WrdKvS33NgNqhg\"><div data-page-id=\"Y4cjdp8M2oYvrUxOMAacYf7JnJd\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\"><div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcn4htBtd03yA81IidYu5vVbe\"><strong>补足核心能力①：</strong><strong>AI</strong><strong>设计能力——跟增长业务怎么结合？</strong></div><div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnVeRhA5usogqSmRLvkTNFYf\">每天都在想\"怎么让更多用户留下来\"。以前靠规则（比如第3天没回来就发push），现在可以用AI做得更精细：用模型预测哪些用户明天会流失、针对不同流失原因生成个性化召回文案。</div><div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnVeRhA5usogqSmRLvkTNFYf\">作为产品经理，不需要自己训练模型，但要能：① 判断\"这个场景用AI比用规则好在哪\"（比如规则只能覆盖5种情况，模型能覆盖500种）；② 写出清晰的AI需求PRD（输入是什么、输出是什么、兜底逻辑是什么）。</div><div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnZZfiYtkTptnjvvXkAXjmBb\"><strong>补足核心能力②：AI工程化与工具链——怎么马上用起来？</strong></div><div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnijdnhm9WowWW9CoHNpnnje\">不等研发排期，自己先用Mira搭一个增长分析workflow：比如每天自动抓取AB实验数据→让AI总结\"哪些实验显著、哪些该关\"→生成日报发群。即入门级的AI工程化能力——不写代码，但能用现成工具把重复劳动自动化。</div><div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnVD5XKtg8wcoCYoMKHWbbkh\"><strong>扩展维度：上下文记忆管理——待核心能力补足后再考虑</strong></div><div class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-doxcnJxhOaGW459KnhI3cPOBpBb\">等核心能力到位、开始做更复杂的AI产品时（比如\"增长知识库\"——让AI基于过去300个实验的经验回答'这个方向上次试过效果怎么样'），就需要理解prompt怎么写、上下文窗口够不够、要不要加检索。</div></div><span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;isCut&quot;:false,&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;Y4cjdp8M2oYvrUxOMAacYf7JnJd&quot;,&quot;parentId&quot;:&quot;doxcnUexl0dMzsJlh5qscF21Zpd&quot;,&quot;blockIds&quot;:[271,272,273,274,275,276],&quot;recordIds&quot;:[&quot;doxcn4htBtd03yA81IidYu5vVbe&quot;,&quot;doxcnVeRhA5usogqSmRLvkTNFYf&quot;,&quot;doxcnZZfiYtkTptnjvvXkAXjmBb&quot;,&quot;doxcnijdnhm9WowWW9CoHNpnnje&quot;,&quot;doxcnVD5XKtg8wcoCYoMKHWbbkh&quot;,&quot;doxcnJxhOaGW459KnhI3cPOBpBb&quot;],&quot;recordMap&quot;:{&quot;doxcn4htBtd03yA81IidYu5vVbe&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;doxcn4htBtd03yA81IidYu5vVbe&quot;,&quot;snapshot&quot;:{&quot;parent_id&quot;:&quot;doxcnUexl0dMzsJlh5qscF21Zpd&quot;,&quot;revisions&quot;:[],&quot;locked&quot;:false,&quot;author&quot;:&quot;7536026773990424595&quot;,&quot;children&quot;:[],&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;核心维度①：AI设计能力——跟增长业务怎么结合？&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0*1+o&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7536026773990424595&quot;],&quot;1&quot;:[&quot;bold&quot;,&quot;true&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:2}},&quot;align&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;comments&quot;:[],&quot;hidden&quot;:false}},&quot;doxcnVeRhA5usogqSmRLvkTNFYf&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;doxcnVeRhA5usogqSmRLvkTNFYf&quot;,&quot;snapshot&quot;:{&quot;children&quot;:[],&quot;align&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;comments&quot;:[],&quot;hidden&quot;:false,&quot;locked&quot;:false,&quot;author&quot;:&quot;7536026773990424595&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0+5a&quot;},&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;你每天都在想\\&quot;怎么让更多用户留下来\\&quot;。以前靠规则（比如第3天没回来就发push），现在可以用AI做得更精细：用模型预测哪些用户明天会流失、针对不同流失原因生成个性化召回文案。你作为产品经理，不需要自己训练模型，但要能：① 判断\\&quot;这个场景用AI比用规则好在哪\\&quot;（比如规则只能覆盖5种情况，模型能覆盖500种）；② 写出清晰的AI需求PRD（输入是什么、输出是什么、兜底逻辑是什么）。&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;nextNum&quot;:1,&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7536026773990424595&quot;]}}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;parent_id&quot;:&quot;doxcnUexl0dMzsJlh5qscF21Zpd&quot;,&quot;revisions&quot;:[]}},&quot;doxcnZZfiYtkTptnjvvXkAXjmBb&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;doxcnZZfiYtkTptnjvvXkAXjmBb&quot;,&quot;snapshot&quot;:{&quot;locked&quot;:false,&quot;hidden&quot;:false,&quot;author&quot;:&quot;7536026773990424595&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;核心维度②：AI工程化与工具链——怎么马上用起来？&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0*1+p&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;nextNum&quot;:2,&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7536026773990424595&quot;],&quot;1&quot;:[&quot;bold&quot;,&quot;true&quot;]}}},&quot;comments&quot;:[],&quot;parent_id&quot;:&quot;doxcnUexl0dMzsJlh5qscF21Zpd&quot;,&quot;revisions&quot;:[],&quot;children&quot;:[],&quot;align&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;}},&quot;doxcnijdnhm9WowWW9CoHNpnnje&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;doxcnijdnhm9WowWW9CoHNpnnje&quot;,&quot;snapshot&quot;:{&quot;align&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;parent_id&quot;:&quot;doxcnUexl0dMzsJlh5qscF21Zpd&quot;,&quot;comments&quot;:[],&quot;revisions&quot;:[],&quot;locked&quot;:false,&quot;hidden&quot;:false,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;nextNum&quot;:1,&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7536026773990424595&quot;]}},&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0+47&quot;},&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;不等研发排期，自己先用Mira搭一个增长分析workflow：比如每天自动抓取AB实验数据→让AI总结\\&quot;哪些实验显著、哪些该关\\&quot;→生成日报发群。这就是入门级的AI工程化能力——不写代码，但能用现成工具把重复劳动自动化。实操建议：先参加一期AI工具实战坊，照着做完\\&quot;用Mira搭自动周报\\&quot;的实操就入门了。&quot;}}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;author&quot;:&quot;7536026773990424595&quot;,&quot;children&quot;:[]}},&quot;doxcnVD5XKtg8wcoCYoMKHWbbkh&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;doxcnVD5XKtg8wcoCYoMKHWbbkh&quot;,&quot;snapshot&quot;:{&quot;revisions&quot;:[],&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;nextNum&quot;:2,&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7536026773990424595&quot;],&quot;1&quot;:[&quot;bold&quot;,&quot;true&quot;]}},&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0*1+l&quot;},&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;扩展维度：上下文记忆管理——什么时候再学？&quot;}}},&quot;align&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;comments&quot;:[],&quot;hidden&quot;:false,&quot;author&quot;:&quot;7536026773990424595&quot;,&quot;children&quot;:[],&quot;parent_id&quot;:&quot;doxcnUexl0dMzsJlh5qscF21Zpd&quot;,&quot;locked&quot;:false}},&quot;doxcnJxhOaGW459KnhI3cPOBpBb&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;doxcnJxhOaGW459KnhI3cPOBpBb&quot;,&quot;snapshot&quot;:{&quot;comments&quot;:[],&quot;revisions&quot;:[],&quot;hidden&quot;:false,&quot;author&quot;:&quot;7536026773990424595&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;等你核心维度到位、开始做更复杂的AI产品时（比如\\&quot;增长知识库\\&quot;——让AI基于过去300个实验的经验回答'这个方向上次试过效果怎么样'），就需要理解prompt怎么写、上下文窗口够不够、要不要加检索。但这是熟练阶段才需要的，入门阶段先不用管。&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0+3c&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7536026773990424595&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:1}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;locked&quot;:false,&quot;children&quot;:[],&quot;align&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;parent_id&quot;:&quot;doxcnUexl0dMzsJlh5qscF21Zpd&quot;}},&quot;doxcnUexl0dMzsJlh5qscF21Zpd&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;doxcnUexl0dMzsJlh5qscF21Zpd&quot;,