      "html": "\n      <header class=\"site-header\">\n        <a class=\"brand\" href=\"index.html\" aria-label=\"AI DRI 指南针首页\">\n          <span class=\"brand-mark compass-mark\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n            <svg viewBox=\"0 0 44 44\" role=\"img\"><circle cx=\"22\" cy=\"22\" r=\"18\"></circle><path d=\"M26.8 17.2 23.9 29l-6.7-2.2 2.9-11.8 6.7 2.2Z\"></path><path d=\"M20.1 15 17.2 26.8l6.7 2.2 2.9-11.8-6.7-2.2Z\"></path><path d=\"M22 5v5M22 34v5M5 22h5M34 22h5\"></path></svg>\n          </span>\n          <span>AI DRI 指南针</span>\n        </a>\n        <nav class=\"nav\" aria-label=\"主导航\">\n          <a data-nav-key=\"guide\" href=\"guide.html\">核心概念</a>\n          <a class=\"active\" data-nav-key=\"map\" href=\"map.html\">能力地图</a>\n          <a data-nav-key=\"cases\" href=\"cases.html\">常见误区</a>\n          <a data-nav-key=\"resources\" href=\"resources.html\">成长路径</a>\n          <a data-nav-key=\"about\" href=\"index.html#about\">关于我们</a>\n        </nav>\n        <div class=\"editor-bar\" aria-label=\"编辑工具栏\">\n          <button class=\"editor-button editor-primary\" type=\"button\" id=\"toggleEdit\">编辑模式<span aria-hidden=\"true\">›</span></button>\n          <button class=\"editor-button\" id=\"saveLocal\" type=\"button\">保存本机</button><button class=\"editor-button\" type=\"button\" id=\"savePage\">发布云端</button>\n          <button class=\"editor-button\" id=\"refreshCloud\" type=\"button\">从云端刷新</button><button class=\"editor-button\" type=\"button\" id=\"exportHtml\">导出 HTML</button>\n          <button class=\"editor-button\" id=\"cloudSettings\" type=\"button\">GitHub 已连接</button><span class=\"save-status\" id=\"saveStatus\" aria-live=\"polite\"></span>\n        </div>\n      </header>\n\n      <main class=\"subpage-main\">\n        <section class=\"subpage-hero\">\n          <p class=\"pill\">指南针体系总览</p>\n          <h1>能力地图</h1>\n          <p><strong style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve; font-size: 1.12rem; font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;\">从认知、核心能力、落地保障到应用提效，全面描绘 AI DRI 的能力地图</strong><div><strong style=\"white-space-collapse: preserve; font-size: 1.12rem; font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;\">本页内容详见</strong>&gt;&gt;文档名</div></p><div>2. 一个图：总结出了核心能力层以外的三个维度的入门、不错、精通，做成表格图</div><div>3. 文档的链接</div><p></p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section class=\"prototype-card map-rotary-card\">\n          <div class=\"map-showcase\">\n            <div class=\"radar-map\" id=\"dimensionWheel\" style=\"--wheel-rotation: 0.00deg;\">\n              <div class=\"radar-ring\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div>\n              <div class=\"radar-axis\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div>\n              <div class=\"radar-center\">AI 时代<br>DRI</div>\n              <button class=\"radar-node active\" type=\"button\" data-dimension=\"0\" style=\"--node-x: 0.0px; --node-y: -250.0px;\"><strong>1</strong><span>用户洞察与问题定义</span></button>\n              <button class=\"radar-node\" type=\"button\" data-dimension=\"1\" style=\"--node-x: 195.5px; --node-y: -155.9px;\"><strong>2</strong><span>领域知识与业务链路理解</span></button>\n              <button class=\"radar-node\" type=\"button\" data-dimension=\"2\" style=\"--node-x: 243.7px; --node-y: 55.6px;\"><strong>3</strong><span>AI 机会判断</span></button>\n              <button class=\"radar-node\" type=\"button\" data-dimension=\"3\" style=\"--node-x: 108.5px; --node-y: 225.2px;\"><strong>4</strong><span>Agent 与工作流编排</span></button>\n              <button class=\"radar-node\" type=\"button\" data-dimension=\"4\" style=\"--node-x: -108.5px; --node-y: 225.2px;\"><strong>5</strong><span>数据、知识与上下文工程</span></button>\n              <button class=\"radar-node\" type=\"button\" data-dimension=\"5\" style=\"--node-x: -243.7px; --node-y: 55.6px;\"><strong>6</strong><span>评估、安全与质量闭环</span></button>\n              <button class=\"radar-node\" type=\"button\" data-dimension=\"6\" style=\"--node-x: -195.5px; --node-y: -155.9px;\"><strong>7</strong><span>产品化、运营与组织推动</span></button>\n            </div>\n            <aside class=\"side-note\">\n              <h2 id=\"dimensionTitle\">机器学习与深度学习</h2>\n              <p id=\"dimensionIntro\"><div data-page-id=\"Jbs4dh9EEo51SpxrXNsckulmn0d\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\"><div class=\" old-record-id-IwYadgfpxoJkAQxDoricqqGAnPg\">能否为业务场景选择合适的模型架构并评估训练效果</div></div><span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;Jbs4dh9EEo51SpxrXNsckulmn0d&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;能否为业务场景选择合适的模型架构并评估训练效果&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0+n&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7586497647800896442&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:1}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;referenceRecordMap&quot;:{},&quot;extra&quot;:{&quot;channel&quot;:&quot;saas&quot;,&quot;isEqualBlockSelection&quot;:false,&quot;pasteRandomId&quot;:&quot;1c848b24-2da5-44ff-a650-c005ae9cde8c&quot;,&quot;mention_page_title&quot;:{},&quot;external_mention_url&quot;:{}},&quot;isKeepQuoteContainer&quot;:false,&quot;isFromCode&quot;:false,&quot;selection&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:189,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;selection&quot;:{&quot;start&quot;:6,&quot;end&quot;:29},&quot;recordId&quot;:&quot;IwYadgfpxoJkAQxDoricqqGAnPg&quot;}],&quot;payloadMap&quot;:{},&quot;isCut&quot;:false}\" data-lark-record-format=\"docx/text\" class=\"lark-record-clipboard\"></span></p>\n              <div class=\"correction-box\">\n                <h3>入门、不错、精通，你要做到什么</h3>\n                <p id=\"dimensionQuestions\"><div data-page-id=\"Jbs4dh9EEo51SpxrXNsckulmn0d\" data-lark-html-role=\"root\" data-docx-has-block-data=\"false\"><ul start=\"1\" class=\"list-bullet1\"><li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-W2PTdayODojRhYxm227c2mS9nHc\" data-list=\"bullet\"><strong>入门</strong>: 了解 CNN/ Transformer/ SFT 等基本概念，能读懂评估报告、参与选型讨论并配合提供标注数据，但不能主导。</li><li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-ICgaddfI3oC1qBxZ95ScTFsDnyg\" data-list=\"bullet\"><strong>不错</strong>: 理解各架构优劣与训练质量标准，能独立制定模型选型策略、设计 A/B 评测体系，并与算法对齐迭代节奏。</li><li class=\"ace-line ace-line old-record-id-KIYdd3ciloBvGbxECjNcBqJznuh\" data-list=\"bullet\"><strong>精通</strong>: 吃透训练全流程与前沿可落地性，能从产品目标反推模型能力、设计端到端迭代飞轮，输出选型方法论。</li></ul></div><span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;isCut&quot;:false,&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;Jbs4dh9EEo51SpxrXNsckulmn0d&quot;,&quot;parentId&quot;:&quot;GJh5dw4pOokHAex89E4cIADSnAh&quot;,&quot;blockIds&quot;:[312,313,314],&quot;recordIds&quot;:[&quot;W2PTdayODojRhYxm227c2mS9nHc&quot;,&quot;ICgaddfI3oC1qBxZ95ScTFsDnyg&quot;,&quot;KIYdd3ciloBvGbxECjNcBqJznuh&quot;],&quot;recordMap&quot;:{&quot;W2PTdayODojRhYxm227c2mS9nHc&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;W2PTdayODojRhYxm227c2mS9nHc&quot;,&quot;snapshot&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;bullet&quot;,&quot;parent_id&quot;:&quot;GJh5dw4pOokHAex89E4cIADSnAh&quot;,&quot;comments&quot;:[],&quot;revisions&quot;:[],&quot;locked&quot;:false,&quot;hidden&quot;:false,&quot;author&quot;:&quot;7586497647800896442&quot;,&quot;children&quot;:[],&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;入门: 了解 CNN/Transformer/SFT 等基本概念，能读懂评估报告、参与选型讨论并配合提供标注数据，但不能主导。&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0*1+2*0+1p&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7586497647800896442&quot;],&quot;1&quot;:[&quot;bold&quot;,&quot;true&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:2}},&quot;align&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;folded&quot;:false}},&quot;ICgaddfI3oC1qBxZ95ScTFsDnyg&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;ICgaddfI3oC1qBxZ95ScTFsDnyg&quot;,&quot;snapshot&quot;:{&quot;type&quot;:&quot;bullet&quot;,&quot;parent_id&quot;:&quot;GJh5dw4pOokHAex89E4cIADSnAh&quot;,&quot;comments&quot;:[],&quot;r